{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Crystal Rail is a roguelite\u00a0train  RPG set in a hand-painted, crystalpunk fantasy world, featuring original music by Jordan Chin (Monster Train)! It blends of the best parts of roguelite strategy with our favorite wild ideas from modern board games.   <br><br><i>If you're not sure what train roguelite gameplay feels like or if you want to know if it's fun, this demo is for you!</i> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose a conductor, inspired by an extinct animal, each with a unique power </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>[demo includes the first 3 characters]:</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482820/extras/CR_CharSelect_small.gif?t=1738369318\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drag cars behind your engine to create your own unique crystal train and set out to strike it rich, <i>by any means necessary!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482820/extras/CR_TrainBuying.gif?t=1738369318\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make deliveries, commission propaganda, send blackmail, and don't forget the oncoming <strong><i>revolution</i></strong>! Anything goes if it leaves you on top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482820/extras/CR_DemRev_Jan232025.gif?t=1738369318\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Last one standing wins!\u00a0<br><br>The full game includes 9 characters, multiple difficulties, dozens of extra train cars, and more! We hope you'll enjoy your time with the demo and wishlist to join us for the full release later this year!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3482820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738369318","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstat